<a href="pathways2.map">
<img ismap src="../icons/npswaste.gif" width=164 height=123 border=0 USEMAP="#pathways map small" alt="pathways navigator graphic"></a>

<table border=0 width=120><tr><td width=60 ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="trans.html" onMouseOver="moveover('Transport'); return true">
<img valign=middle width=45 height=36 border=0 src="../icons/nitransc.gif" alt="Transport"></a>

</td><td width=60 ALIGN=CENTER>
<A HREF="waste.html" onMouseOver="moveover('Current Page'); return true"><img valign=middle width=40 height=23 border=0 src="../icons/nwasteh.gif" alt="Waste"></a>

</td></tr></table>

<!--ASPECT OPTIONS TABLE--------------------------------------------------->
<BR>
<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=160 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2>
<TR><TD align=center bgcolor=FF595B>
<font face="arial" size=+0><a href="waste01.html">More Information</a>
</TD></TR>
<!--TR><TD align=center bgcolor=AAAAEE>
<font face="arial" size=+0><a href="waste.html">Campaign History</a>
</TD></TR--></TABLE>

<END OF LEFT COLUMN---------------------------------------------------------->

<TD WIDTH=400 VALIGN=TOP>

<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=100% HEIGHT=70>
<TR><TD  VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT SIZE=+2 FACE="MS SERIF">N U C L E A R  &nbspW A S T E </FONT>


</TD></TR></TABLE>

<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=390><TR><TD VALIGN=TOP>

<FONT SIZE=+0 FACE="MS SERIF">


<P>Nuclear waste is produced at every stage of the nuclear fuel cycle, from uranium mining 
to reactors to the reprocessing of irradiated nuclear fuel.  Much of this nuclear waste will 
remain hazardous for thousands of years, leaving a poisonous legacy to future 
generations.  

<p>Dangerous radioactive isotopes such as caesium, strontium, iodine, krypton and 
plutonium are created when operating a nuclear reactor. Plutonium is particularly 
dangerous in that it can be used in nuclear weapons if it is separated from the irradiated 
nuclear fuel in a chemical treatment called reprocessing. 

</FONT>
<br><br>
</TD></TR></TABLE>
 
</TD></TR></TABLE>

