http://greenpeace.org:80/~climate/ctb/update94.html 193.67.176.1 19970103134958 text/html 8645
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 13:52:37 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
