<FONT SIZE=-1>
<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
<A HREF="http://www.unep.ch/iucc/fs005.html">Is the Earth warming up yet?</A>
<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
<A HREF="http://www.unep.ch/iucc/fs105.html">Will climate change lead to more extremes and disasters?</A>  
 <DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
<A HREF="http://www.unep.ch/iucc/fs238.html">Insurance against climate change?</A>  
<BR>
