<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
<A HREF="http://www.unep.ch/iucc/fs008.html">Why three hot summers don't mean global warming?</A>
<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
