<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
<A HREF="http://www.unep.ch/iucc/fs237.html">A 'responsibility index' for climate change.</A> 
<DT><IMG ALIGN=MIDLE SRC="gpdotsmsm.gif">
