<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=5 SRC="germana1.gif" ALT="Greenpeace Activists Climb Rwe's Smokestack>
<DT>This is where you'll find
the daily Greenpeace view on the twists and turns of the Berlin
Summit,  as the governments of the world wheel and deal with the future of
our planet. Greenpeace correspondent Cindy Baxter reports.<BR>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
<A NAME="top"><IMG ALIGN=middle BORDER=0 SRC="gpdotup.gif" ALT="Top of Page Icon"></A> = Top of this page
</P>
<HR>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
04/07/95 - <A HREF="berlin.html#report6">Climate Summit Fails To Combat Climate Change</A>
 | 
04/05/95 - <A HREF="berlin.html#report5">Greenpeace: Kohl Speech Full Of Rethoric And Promises,
US Still Blocking Political Breakthrough In Berlin</A>
 | 
