were arrested today at the Cargill grain terminal for protesting the companies
export of genetically engineered soybeans.  The activists (Peter Bradley,

Anibal Rivera, Monica Rhode, David DeRosa, Tanya Whitford) have been charged
with criminal trespass and violation of a restraining order and are still being
