<head>
   <title>MACMILLAN BLOEDEL CUTS GREENPEACE ACTIVISTS
FREE, GREENPEACE GIVES CHASE

</title>
   
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="CCCCFC" TEXT="130036" LINK="D51C27" VLINK="970000" ALINK="E200A9">

<table border=1 cellpadding=5 width=100%>
<tr>
<td><a href="canada.html"><img src="../icons/biofor.gif" border=2 height=80 width=60 align=left></a><a href="newsindx.html#barge"><img src="../icons/bionews.gif" border=0 height=60 width=60 align=right></a></td>
