contribute a minimum of US$500 for each company.  In addition it 
has invited all Members of IFOMA to donate a minimum of US$2,000.


In the event that the campaign fund is not fully utilised the 
remaining funds will be redistributed to the contributors pro-
rata to their contribution.
 
IFOMA has prepared the first in a series of defence documents 
describing the present practices of industrial fishing in the 
