                    	<A HREF="actindx.html#actw01"><img align=right border=0 width=50 height=50
                     	src="../icons/bioact.gif"></a>
                    	<font size=+1><B>GREENPEACE BLOCKADE OF NORWEGIAN WHALERS ENDS 
	    	 AS LOCAL THUGS THREATEN VIOLENCE.</B></font></td>
	</tr>
</table>


<blockquote>
<p>40 Greenpeace activists from six nations (Norway, Sweden, Finland, Denmark, UK and Germany,) blockaded four Norwegian whaling vessels (Villduen, Seie, Senet and Seiebuen) to prevent them leaving port.  Activists secured themselves to the railings of one whaling ships and tied floating blue rope through three of the vessels.  Other activists remained in the water with buoys blocking their exit and held up a banner reading "NORWAY STOP WHALING."  
<BR><BR>
</blockquote>


