<body>

<h2>DIARIES FROM ABOARD THE RAINBOW WARRIOR AND MV GREENPEACE</h2>

<p>

<P>JUNE 16th - <a href="jun16d.html"><I> A wild sort of night, gusting to 40 knots (with pictures).</I></a>

<br>JUNE 18th - <a href="jun18d.html"><I> We have decided to put in to Rarotonga, capital of the Cook Islands (with pictures). </I></a>

<br>JUNE 19th - <a href="jun19d.html"><I>Best weather we've seen yet on our voyage (with pictures).</I></a>

