<br>JULY 13th - <a href="jul13d.html"><I>The good news keeps flooding in:</I></a>

<br>JULY 19th - <a href="jul19d.html"><I>150 miles from Rarotonga, ETA there tomorrow morning. Official function with PM and opposition MPs, on Thursday night.</I></a>

<br>August 5th - <a href="aug05d.html"><I>Health in French Polynesia: A Medicins sans Frontieres team questions the effects of French Nuclear Testing.</I></a>

