<br>Islas Marquisas Ua-Huka        345 miles, 120 degrees left of PP
<br>Tahiti          Papeete      1,100 miles, 100 degrees left of PP
<br>Kiribati        Bairiki      3,010 miles, 45 degrees left of PP
<br>Nauru           Nauru Island 3,380 miles, 45 degrees left of PP
<br>Western Samoa   Apia         2,150 miles, 65 degrees left of PP
