<br>Tahiti       Papeete        2,020  miles, 150 degrees left of PP
<br>Kiribati     Bairiki        1,800  miles, 65 degrees left of PP
<br>Nauru        Nauru Island   2,190  miles, 65 degrees left of PP
<br>Western Samoa   Apia        1,850  miles, 115 degrees left of PP
<br>American Samoa  Pago Pago   1,840  miles, 110 degrees left of PP
<br>Tonga           Nuku'Alofa  2,310  miles, 110 degrees left of PP
<br>Tuvalu       Funafuti       1,890  miles, 90 degrees left of PP
<br>Fiji            Suva        2,360  miles, 100 degrees left of PP
<br>Solomon Isl.    Honiara     2,820  miles, 70 degrees left of PP
<br>Vanuatu       Palikulo Bay  2,690  miles, 80 degrees left of PP
