<TITLE>Becoming a supporter of Greenpeace</TITLE>
<LINK REV="MADE" HREF="sysop@xs2.greenpeace.org">
<h2>Support Greenpeace</h2>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">
<hr>
<br>
Go direct to the "how to support" page of a national office:
<ul>

<li> <img width=32 height=32 src="/pics/austrlia.gif" alt="Ozzies: "> <a 
href="http://www.sofcom.com.au/Greenpeace/how2get.html">Greenpeace 
Australia</a></li> 

<li> <img width=32 height=32 src="/pics/italy.gif" alt="Italia: "> <a 
href="http://www.videomusic.com/ambiente/greenpeace/asso.htm">Greenpeace 
Italy</a></li> 

<li> <img width=32 height=32 src="/pics/norway.gif" alt="Norge: "> <a 
href="http://www.oslonett.no/~greenp/premedl.html">Greenpeace Norway</a></li>

<li> <img width=32 height=19 src="/pics/ssweden.gif" alt="Sverig: "> <a 
href="/~sweden/div/support.html">Greenpeace Sweden</a></li>

</ul>
Or fill out a donation form (in English) to one of the following:
<ul>
<li> Contact a Greenpeace <b>office</b> such as USA, Germany, Argentina, etc., 
select:</li> <p><ul>
<li> <a href="allcontr.html">This form if you have a Netscape or Prodigy</a> 
(CompuServe) compatible browser,</li> 
<li> or <a href="fix-allcontr.html"> this form for Lynx or AOL</a> (America On Line) 
compatible browser;</li> </ul> 
</ul></ul> Or, if there is <b>no</b> Greenpeace office in your country:
<ul>
<li><b>Supporter Services</b> at <a href="gpicontr.html">Greenpeace 
International</a> (i.e. NOT for USA please)</li></ul>
<p>
